    ///   without allocating either `Vec<ConfigSourceKind>`. On the
    ///   cardinality-`3` layer-kind axis the two equalities are
    ///   disjoint (`1 ŌēĀ 2 = cardinality - 1`) and the disjunction
    ///   reads the true dual.
