    /// disjunct) and on every uniform three-kind cover (three observed
    /// cells ŌĆö full-cover disjunct), and `false` on every singleton-
    /// support chain (support cardinality `1` ŌĆö one nonzero and two
    /// zeros mixed) and every two-kind partial cover (support
    /// cardinality `2` ŌĆö two nonzeros and one zero mixed, exactly the
