    /// **Empty-chain convention** ŌĆö returns `true` on the empty chain:
    /// the empty chain observes zero cells, so every cell is
    /// unobserved (three zeros on the cardinality-`3` axis) ŌĆö the
    /// single-pass scan sees no nonzero cell and falls through to
