    ///   equality form on the two named cardinality peers, the
    ///   `present + absent == axis_cardinality` invariant restated.
    /// - `!layer_kinds_any_observed() ŌćÆ layer_kinds_boundary()` always
    ///   ŌĆö the empty chain sits on the boundary via the bottom
    ///   disjunct.
    /// - `layer_kinds_full_cover() ŌćÆ layer_kinds_boundary()` always ŌĆö
    ///   the full-cover chain sits on the boundary via the top
    ///   disjunct.
    /// - `layer_kinds_boundary() ŌćÆ !layer_kinds_singular()` on every
    ///   axis with cardinality `>= 2`: the two boundary cardinalities
