    /// interior bucket
    /// [`crate::SupportMagnitudeDirection::StrictInterior`] is
    /// **vacuously unreachable** on the cardinality-`3` layer-kind
    /// sub-axis ŌĆö the underlying strict-partial-cover corner is itself
