    /// file_formats_strictly_modally_unique` ŌĆö the strict-uniqueness
    /// pair collapses to a single boolean, the singleton-support
    /// witness. Direct pin of the histogram-side collapse law
    /// `is_uniform_count Ōł¦ !is_empty ŌćÆ is_strictly_antimodally_unique Ōćö
    /// is_strictly_modally_unique` one altitude down ŌĆö the strict-
    /// uniqueness-side peer of the tie-side collapse
