        // `layer_kinds_high_support_implies_layer_kinds_any_observed_pointwise`
        // on the layer-kind sub-axis of the same chain altitude,
        // `tiers_high_support_implies_tiers_any_observed_pointwise`
        // on the tier altitude, and
